race.comment: GAME OF PHONES (1) was sent out long odds last time but rocketed out of the boxes with a fast early sectional and gave a sight before being swallowed up late, finishing a 2 length second (23.07) over 400m at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Top prospect. AMRON TOMMY (4) latest effort finished 3rd on November 6 over 460m at this track behind Mia Neo beaten 4 lengths (26.19) in a Grade 4/5. Can feature with the right run. TARGET RANGE (2) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing eighth (26.68) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including four wins. Can figure in the finish. JUMPING OREO (3) cannot be written off despite a miss here at her latest outing.
